node.html: Develop and enhance the accuracy of ML models, ensuring more precise predictions that could significantly improve Airbnb's market positioning and customer satisfaction strategies.
Developed a BERT language model to predict the topic of user posts on Stack Exchange sites with an impressive test accuracy of 96.9%.
Designed and implemented a scalable database for an online laptop store, resulting in a notable 30% improvement in data management efficiency.
Spearheaded the analysis of 2M+ real-time records across 15+ features, and while maintaining data quality, analyzed songs released in 2022 to compare how music preferences have changed over time.
